{"tid":1956873,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"日日留係屋企 想做d有意義既野 求idea","createTime":"2020-04-03T13:10:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T13:20:46.000Z","uid":355065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5a79b3e03acd961ccbcc9899784ddbf400e87715","tid":1956873,"uid":355065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T13:10:20.000Z","msg":"第一次出post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申宜家係歐洲生活<br />\n封城封左三個星期<br />\nWork at home 左三個星期<br />\n日日起身就開會開8個鐘<br />\n跑步又無得去<br />\n開完會就上fb/YouTube/Netflix 玩到眼訓就訓<br />\n覺得好浪費人生<br />\n<br />\n係到識左個藝術家<br />\n日日佢邀請人上網傾計<br />\n紀錄quarantine 既生活<br />\n再畫埋人像畫去紀錄<br />\n<br />\n好有意義<br />\n可惜我畫畫唔叻<br />\n<br />\n唔知可以點充實呢段日子<br />\n仲有一個月挨<br />\n<br />\n日日困係屋企 又無咩朋友可以傾計<br />\n覺得就黎痴線 好似好耐無同真正既人交流咁<br />\n我諗唔少獨住既人都有同樣感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n求idea <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02199583cbabf6bdf10e39de978d3c6fe793278d","tid":1956873,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T13:11:26.000Z","msg":"用龜頭畫一幅圖"},{"pid":"aa35a83645717018cdc9c13d551c52f1cadbffed","tid":1956873,"uid":355065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"02199583cbabf6bdf10e39de978d3c6fe793278d","tid":1956873,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T13:11:26.000Z","msg":"用龜頭畫一幅圖"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T13:12:54.000Z","msg":"可以我係絲"},{"pid":"82506d27ae537e6038d408e5b83764b0de2779a5","tid":1956873,"uid":134863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aa35a83645717018cdc9c13d551c52f1cadbffed","tid":1956873,"uid":355065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"02199583cbabf6bdf10e39de978d3c6fe793278d","tid":1956873,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T13:11:26.000Z","msg":"用龜頭畫一幅圖"},"ci